itemDescription: Miss Cayman Islands 2010, contestant in Miss Universe 2011 and Miss World 2010

wikipedia_page.main: Cristin Joy Alexander (born c. 1987) is a beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss Cayman Islands 2010. She represented Cayman Islands at  Miss Universe 2011 and Miss World 2010.
